Invocation Name: honeyfi
des:
Get quick updates on how you and your partner are doing from Honeyfi.

Try saying:
Alexa, ask Honeyfi how are we doing this month
Alexa, ask Honeyfi to start our money date
Alexa, ask Honeyfi if we have any upcoming bills
Alexa, ask Honeyfi for the most recent transactions
Alexa, ask Honeyfi where is our money going

Please let us know what you think and what else you'd like to see!
